# Exception: ship the latest CRITIC artifacts as a cockpit seed. Railway
# containers are ephemeral, so without these committed the Spirit-vs-Letter
# panel would be blank on first deploy. Refresh by running `npm run critic`
# locally and committing the new files.
!data/rules-proposal.yaml
!data/critic-reports/
!data/critic-reports/*.md
data/observation-pass/
